songs.title: Mineral Minaj

Cathy errors (cathy), hey you want sum mo (sum mo)?
Lovely terrors (hatefull), I feel so mineral (Minaj)
Feel so mineral (yeah, yeah)
Feel so mineral (yeah, ya)
I feel so mineral (Minaj)
Cause I feel (feel, feel, feel)
Such a mineral Mina-

Queen is back
Nicki cap
GOATing rap
Beefy crap
Love for life
He a lie
She a psy

Bitch please learn being kind

For talent girl
I'm back so you should leave (go)
Since I dubbed a bitch in Pieve (bitch in Pieve, Pieve)

[Chorus]
Cathy errors, hey you want sum mo?

Cathy errors (cathy), hey you want sum mo (sum mo)?
Lovely terrors (hatefull), I feel so mineral (Minaj)
Feel so mineral (yeah, yeah)
Feel so mineral (yeah, ya)
I feel so mineral (Minaj)
Cause I feel (feel, feel, feel)
Such a mineral Mina-

[Verse 2]
Lovely laugh
Still the half
Drive the boat
They asked for the GOAT
I showed up ho
Passed all ya haters no (nope)
A hole in yo dreams
Nobody here still seems
Bringin tinz, lick it all the way inz

[Pre-Chorus]
It's a challenge girl (hey)
For talent girl
I'm back so you should leave (go)
Since I dubbed a bitch in Pieve (bitch in Pieve)

[Chorus]
Cathy errors, hey you want sum mo?

Cathy errors (cathy), hey you want sum mo (sum mo)?
Lovely terrors (hateful), I feel so mineral (Minaj)
Feel so mineral (yeah, yeah)
Feel so mineral (yeah, ya)
I feel so mineral (Minaj)
Cause I feel (feel, feel, feel)

[Outro]
They need Nicki in da game
They need MeE in da gang
Love you haters (haters, haters, haters, haters)
